org.yatech.jedis.utils.lua

Class LuaPreparedScript

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.yatech.jedis.utils.lua.LuaScript
      • org.yatech.jedis.utils.lua.LuaPreparedScript

  • public class LuaPreparedScript
extends LuaScript
    A prepared script which can have a fixed script with argument placeholders. The placeholders can be set with concrete values and then the script can be executed without the need to rebuild it. Created by Yinon Avraham on 11/09/2015.
    See Also:
    LuaScriptBuilder.endPreparedScript()
